# Startup Performance Dashboard

This project creates an interactive web-based dashboard using Dash and Plotly to visualize startup performance data. The dashboard includes four charts (Pie, Bar, Scatter, and Bubble) with dynamic filters for sector, region, and funding stage. It also exports a static HTML snapshot for sharing.

## Table of Contents
- [Project Overview](#project-overview)
- [Features](#features)
